snippet.title: Best VGM 1839 - Mega Man Battle Network 5 : Double Team - Network Space (Internet Area)
snippet.description:
A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Nintendo DS
Mega Man Battle Network 5 : Double Team (2005)
Network Space (Internet Area)
Mitsuhiko Takano, Seiko Kobuchi & Yoshino Aoki
